-- Village Playback Theatre Actors Talk Therapeutic Drama (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-05-31T22:23:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-31/village-playback-theatre-actors-talk-therapeutic-drama-audio-.html
 Randy Mulder, artistic director of 
the Village Playback Theatre in  New York  City's East Village, 
explains VPT's methodology: improvising scenes based on stories 
elicited from audience members. Mulder is joined by VPT 
performers Katie Lear and Dan Guerra. They speak with 
Bloomberg's Kathleen Hays and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's 
"The Hays Advantage."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 12:09
 